THE J-JUNCTION · node JJ1 · JJ1 · Governance is a vector that only becomes governance where it crosses. Pure authority is an isolated tower; pure connection is an ungoverned field; governance is the dot between them — gated by a valve, watched by a witness, holding device and risk in the same point. <• is the primitive: every junction in the whole corpus is this one shape.

